         <section class="grid-block" id="content">
          <div id="system-message-container">
          </div>
          <div id="system">
           <article class="item">
            <header>
             <h1 class="title">
              Our Practice Areas
             </h1>
            </header>
            <div class="content clearfix">
             <p>
              At Baron &amp; Stagger chambers, we offer a wide range of legal services to our clients. Our practice areas include:
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:6.0pt;">
              ·         Aviation
              <br />
                        Banking and Finance
              <img align="right" src="/images/law-book-small.png" alt="" class="size-auto" />
              <br />
                        Business Fraud
              <br />
                        Business Re-organisation and Insolvency
              <br />
                        Corporate &amp; Commercial
              <br />
                        Criminal Law Procedure and Practice
              <br />
                        Energy and Natural Resources
              <br />
                        Environmental
              <br />
                        Infrastructure
              <br />
                        Insurance
              <br />
                        Intellectual Property
              <br />
                        Labour &amp; Employment
              <br />
                        Litigation and Dispute Resolution
              <br />
                        Maritime
              <br />
                        Probate Practice
              <br />
                        Real Estate and Property Law
              <br />
                        Taxation
             </p>
             <p>
              <strong>
               FINANCING EXPERIENCE
              </strong>
             </p>
             <p>
              Our lawyers have participated in projects in the oil and gas, power, mining, telecommunications, infrastructure and engineering, tourism and manufacturing industries.
             </p>
             <p>
              We have provided comprehensive financial advice to international and Nigerian financial/lending institutions, commercial, merchant and investment banks, leasing companies, insurance companies, mortgage institutions, brokerage and investment companies and other financial institutions. We have represented and worked with export credit agencies, multilateral agencies and development finance institutions.
             </p>
             <p>
              We have acted for project lenders or sponsors in several limited and non- recourse cross border financings involving multiple parties. We have worked cordially and efficiently with foreign legal and other technical advisers and are committed to partnering with you to provideprofessional services of the highest quality at a reasonable cost.
             </p>
             <p>
              Some of the transactions in which our lawyers have been involved include:
             </p>
             <p>
              <strong>
               <u>
                Oil and gas / reserves-based financings
               </u>
              </strong>
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
              ·         Advising promoters in the financing and establishment of a natural gas liquefaction project within a Free Trade Zone.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
              ·         Legal Adviser to an indigenous oil company on a US$20 Million term loan financing of debt and the development of oil wells on an oil mining lease.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
              ·      Provided legal and commercial advice on the financing of the exploration and development of a goldmine in Ilesa, Osun State as well as tin mining in Jos, Plateau State.
             </p>
             <p>
              ·         Counsel to the Sponsors on the financing and structure of a joint venture and other collaboration arrangements for the    
              <br />
                    development of a Greenfield export - oriented petroleum refinery.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
              ·         In collaboration with foreign lawyers, acting for and advising a group of International Banks on aspects of the financing of a Petrochemical Plant.
             </p>
             <p>
              <strong>
               <u>
                Acquisitions financing comprising multilateral financing sources
               </u>
              </strong>
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
               ·    Nigerian Counsel to the sponsors of a US$ 1.6 billion syndicated limited recourse project financing involving Nigerian and foreign commercial banks in respect of the construction, operation and maintenance of an International Estate in Isagara/Ikare Island, Lagos State.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
               ·  Nigerian Legal Counsel to Export Credit Agencies (ECAs) and ECA Lenders in series of ECA-supported $260 million financing of three Airbus aircraft.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
               ·       Co-ordinated the documentation for the financing of the the three Airbus aircrafts.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
               ·       Legal Consultant to the Vendor on the acquisition of two oil service companies.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
               ·       Advising on securing perfection of financing package for the acquisition by a client of a floating storage vessel.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
              ·        Advising on a number of banking and financial transactions including structuring and drafting of equipment leases and sale and lease back contracts.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
               ·    Preparation of loan agreements, advice on Security Documentation, drafting and review of Security Documents including, but not limited to, legal mortgages, debentures (fixed and floating) bills of sale, mortgage debentures, pledges, guarantees and indemnities.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
               ·      Conducted due diligence including advise on a myriad of documentation including memorandum and articles of association, shareholders agreement, hotel management agreement.
             </p>
             <p>
              <strong>
               ENERGY &amp; NATURAL RESOURCES
              </strong>
             </p>
             <p>
              <strong>
               (a)
               <u>
                 Oil and Gas
               </u>
              </strong>
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
              ·         Legal Adviser to promoters of a gas supply and pricing aggregation project.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
              ·        Advising international oil company on direct foreign investment in Nigeria and the acquisition of upstream and  downstream oil assets.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
               ·         Negotiating farm-out of marginal oil field with major international oil company.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
               ·     Advised international oil company on regulatory compliance issues in respect of its investment in an offshore export free zone.
             </p>
             <p>
              <strong>
               (b) 
               <u>
                Mining
               </u>
              </strong>
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
               ·         Advising and assisting a mining company in the establishment of a Nigerian subsidiary and the  acquisition of mineral titles.
             </p>
             <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;">
               ·         Advising a mining corporation on the acquisition of majority interest in several exploration licences.
             </p>
             <p>
              INCORPORATION/COMPANY SECRETARIAL
             </p>
             <p>
              BARON &amp; STAGGER CHAMBERS regularly advises clients on the investment climate in Nigeria and the appropriate structure of investment options to suit their needs, either direct or portfolio. We assist clients to establish presence in Nigeria in a tax-efficient structure. We procure relevant licences and approvals. BARON &amp; STAGGER CHAMBERS provides company secretary services to desiring clients.
             </p>
            </div>
           </article>
          </div>
         </section>
